# ========================================
# Abaco Office Add-in - Environment Variables
# ========================================
# 
# ‚ö†Ô∏è  SECURITY WARNING: Never commit real API keys or tokens!
# ‚úÖ Use GitHub Codespaces Secrets or environment variables
# 
# To set up:
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Fill in your actual credentials in .env
